###
# ============================================================
# SUBSCRIPTIONS — NO AUTH
# ============================================================

### [33] Get subscriptions — no auth → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions

### [34] Create subscription — no auth → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan_id": 1,
  "billing_cycle": "monthly"
}

###
# ============================================================
# SUBSCRIPTIONS — WITH USER TOKEN
# ============================================================

### [35] Create subscription — user (first time, gets trial) → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "plan_id": 1,
  "billing_cycle": "monthly"
}

### [36] Create subscription again — user (already active/trialing) → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "plan_id": 1,
  "billing_cycle": "monthly"
}

### [37] Get my subscriptions — user → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### [38] Get subscription details — user (own) → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### [39] Cancel subscription — user (own) → 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### [40] Cancel already canceled — user → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### [41] Cancel subscription of another user — user → 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
# ============================================================
# SUBSCRIPTIONS — WITH ADMIN TOKEN
# ============================================================

### [42] Get all subscriptions — admin → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [43] Activate subscription — admin → 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [44] Activate already active — admin → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [45] Mark past due — admin → 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/mark-past-due
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [46] Renew subscription — user → 403 (system only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/renew
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### [47] Expire subscription — admin → 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1/expire
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [48] Extend period — admin → 200
PUT {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "current_period_ends_at": "2027-01-01 00:00:00"
}

### [49] Extend period — user → 403
PUT {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "current_period_ends_at": "2027-01-01 00:00:00"
}

###
# ============================================================
# SUBSCRIPTION TRANSACTIONS — NO AUTH
# ============================================================

### [50] Get transactions — no auth → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions

###
# ============================================================
# SUBSCRIPTION TRANSACTIONS — ADMIN
# ============================================================

### [51] Create transaction — admin → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "subscription_id": 1,
  "provider": "manual"
}

### [52] Create transaction — user → 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "subscription_id": 1
}

### [53] Get all transactions — admin → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [54] Get transaction — user (own subscription) → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### [55] Mark paid — admin (auto-activates subscription) → 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions/1/mark-paid
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [56] Mark paid again — admin → 422 (not pending)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions/1/mark-paid
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [57] Mark failed — admin → 422 (already paid)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions/1/mark-failed
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "failure_reason": "Card declined"
}

### [58] Refund — admin → 200 (adds amount back to user balance)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions/1/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [59] Refund again — admin → 422 (not paid)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions/1/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### [60] Get my transactions — user → 200 (max 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
